name: Debt Collection Detail
query:
select 
client As "Client:Data:120", 
cell_phone_no as "CellPhone:Data:120",
customer as "Customer:Link/Customer:150",
amount as "Amount:Currency:100",
service_type as "Service Type:Link/Debt Service Type:100",
paid_amount as "Paid Amount:Currency:100",
agent as "Agent:Link/Sales Person:120",
receive_date as "Receive Date:Date:100",
next_call_date as "Next Call Date:Date:100",
status as "Status:Link/Client Debt Status:100"
from `tabClient Debt`
